        <p><milestone unit="page" n="962" facs="994:1"/>
      <cb n="2"/>
      <lb n="11"/>duḥ<ruby><rb>khī</rb><rt>na</rt></ruby> tri duḥkhitaḥ | yathā |</p>
        <lg corresp="VP65.47">
          <l><lb n="12"/>duḥkhino 'duḥkhino vāpi <lb n="13"/>prāṇino labdhacakṣuṣaḥ |</l>
          <l>ātmavat <lb n="14"/>paripaśyanti te yānti paramāṃ <lb n="15"/>gatiṃ ||</l>
        </lg>
        <lg corresp="VP65.56">
          <l>tyaktvātmasukhabhoge<lb n="16"/>cchāṃ sarvvasattvasukhaiṣiṇaḥ |</l>
          <l>bhava<lb n="17"/>nti paraduḥkhena sādhavo nitya<lb n="18"/>duḥkhitāḥ ||</l>
        </lg>
        <p>iti vahnipurāṇe <lb n="19"/>śiver upākhyānanāmādhyāyaḥ ||</p>
